title: Quick Keen3-related flash
content:
I've been told by somebody that an old Cosmo parody I did was posted here, or somewhere in the community, or whatever. You can see that... waait for it... [url=http://www.yossarko.com/wdfaa/files/cosmo.swf]HERE.[/url]

So I was bored enough recently to make a Keen 3 thingy. It's quick, pointless, and has a reference to a certain cartoon movie. A pointless one, in fact.

[url=http://img213.echo.cx/my.php?image=keen2jc.swf]Click here[/url] to view it. You could also [url=http://img213.echo.cx/my.php?image=keen2jc.swf]click here[/url] to view it too, but it goes to the same URL, so there isn't much point.

Let me know what you guys think. Oh, and while I'm here, hi Sluggy! [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-poisonslug.gif[/img]
